♪ <i>This is for all the lonely people</i> ♪

41:53.346 --> 41:55.974
♪ <i>Thinking that life has passed them by</i> ♪

41:59.394 --> 42:02.355
♪ <i>Don't give up until you</i> ♪

42:02.439 --> 42:05.066
♪ <i>Drink from the silver cup</i> ♪

42:05.150 --> 42:08.319
♪ <i>And ride that highway in the sky</i> ♪

42:10.447 --> 42:14.492
♪ <i>Well, I'm on my way back home</i> ♪

42:15.994 --> 42:17.454
♪ <i>Hit it</i> ♪

