42:39.934 --> 42:42.937
♪ <i>Don't give up until you</i> ♪

42:43.021 --> 42:45.940
♪ <i>Drink from the silver cup</i> ♪

42:46.024 --> 42:49.235
♪ <i>And never take you down or</i> ♪

42:49.319 --> 42:51.988
♪ <i>Never give you up</i> ♪

